#. module: beverage_distributor
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:beverage_distributor.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Collect deposits when you deliver to your customer. It is easy. When "
"validating your delivery, you can directly set a \"Return\" and precisely "
"count the number of each type of deposit your customer gave you. It will "
"automatically be reflected on his invoice or issue a credit note."
msgstr ""
