#. module: beverage_distributor
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:beverage_distributor.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"On a regular basis, excises need to be declared. To support you with this "
"duty, a report generated weekly provides the quantity by excise category "
"entering and exiting your fiscal deposit warehouse with a dedicated activity "
"for it."
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍປົກກະຕິ, ພາສີຊົມໃຊ້ຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການແຈ້ງ. ເພື່ອສະໜັບສະໜູນທ່ານໃນໜ້າທີ່ນີ້, "
"ລະບົບຈະສ້າງລາຍງານປະຈຳອາທິດເຊິ່ງໃຫ້ຂໍ້ມູນປະລິມານຕາມໝວດໝູ່ພາສີຊົມໃຊ້ ທີ່ນຳເຂົ້າ ແລະ "
"ນຳອອກຈາກສາງພາສີຊົມໃຊ້ຂອງທ່ານ ໂດຍມີກິດຈະກຳສະເພາະສຳລັບວຽກນັ້ນ."

#. module: beverage_distributor
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:beverage_distributor.welcome_article_body
